12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 56 O.S. 2021, Section 4001.5, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 4001.5. A. Account balances and distributions from
16 savings accounts established pursuant to this act shall be exempt
17 from levy and sale, garnishment, attachment or any other process
18 whatsoever and shall be unassignable. In the event of the death of
19 a beneficiary, the funds from an Achieving a Better Life Experience
20 (ABLE) account are also exempt from Medicaid recovery liens, claim,
21 and other reimbursement proceedings filed pursuant to Section 12-
22 994.2 of Title 12 of the Oklahoma Statutes by the Oklahoma Health
23 Care Authority.
