1 B. Money and assets residing in an account established pursuant
2 to this act or residing in an ABLE account established in another
3 state shall not be considered for purposes of determining
4 eligibility for assistance or benefits or for determining the amount
5 of assistance or benefits to be received from the Temporary
6 Assistance for Needy Families program or from any other local or
7 state means-tested public assistance programs.
8 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
